author: dims
msg: Handle the case when we start axis servlet with both http and https on in tomcat's conf/server.xml (say 5050 for http and 5443 for https) and the user types in the url for dynamic wsdl - https://localhost:5443/axis2/services/Version?wsdl in the browser. W/O this patch we were returning just one wsdl:port and that too pointing to http://localhost:8080/
